1RapCorona (feat. Mel) - Knox Artiste

Watch as Knox Artiste along with his friends from YouTube and his fans make your lockdown a little bit more entertaining with his brand new video – RapCorona featuring a very special talent from Dubai – Mel

We’d like to thank Dr. Ray Ednie along with Doctors and all other Healthcare Professionals, Drivers & Delivery personnel, Grocery workers, and Restaurant workers helping to keep us fed during this crisis along with all the government personnel like police officers, emergency response teams and sanitization crews working towards the end of the pandemic!

ALSO AVAILABLE ON:

Jio Saavn: https://bit.ly/RapCoronaJioSaavn

Wynk Music App: https://bit.ly/RapCoronaWynk

Gaana: https://bit.ly/RapCoronaGaana

Hungama: https://bit.ly/RapCoronaHungama
